lation. Explosive) is a 2020 Indian [[Hindi]]-language Romantic Action film. Directed by Ranjan Chandel starring debutant Aditya Rawal and Shalini Pandey in their first lead film. The official trailer was unveiled on 06 April 2020 and film was released on 10 April 2020. \n\nIt is passionate love story set in Allahabad between Naseer<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.indiatoday.in/movies/celebrities/story/paresh-rawal-s-son-aditya-will-take-me-30-years-to-be-spoken-of-in-same-breath-as-dad-1665053-2020-04-09|title=Paresh Rawal's son Aditya: Will take me 30 years to be spoken of in same breath as dad|last=India|first=Today|date=9 April 2020|website=Indiatoday|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200410081224/https://www.indiatoday.in/movies/celebrities/story/paresh-rawal-s-son-aditya-will-take-me-30-years-to-be-spoken-of-in-same-breath-as-dad-1665053-2020-04-09|archive-date=10 April 2020|access-date=2020-04-07}}</ref>a.k.a. Naate and Neelam who meet accidentally and fall in love. They make brave choices and go through a path of love and loss to be with each other.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cinestaan.com/articles/2020/apr/4/25206/now-paresh-rawal-s-son-aditya-is-set-to-make-his-acting-debut-with-bamfaad-on-zee5|title=Now, Paresh Rawal's son Aditya is set to make his acting debut with Bamfaad on Zee5|last=|first=|date=4 April 2020|website=Cinestaan|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200407064853/https://www.cinestaan.com/articles/2020/apr/4/25206/now-paresh-rawal-s-son-aditya-is-set-to-make-his-acting-debut-with-bamfaad-on-zee5|archive-date=7 April 2020|access-date=2020-04-07}}</ref>\n\n==Cast==\n* Aditya Rawal as Nasir Jamal<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://zeetv.zee5.com/bamfaad-heres-what-you-need-to-know-about-the-upcoming-zee5-original-film/|title=Bamfaad: Here\u2019s What You Need To Know About The Upcoming ZEE5 Original Film|date=2020-04-04|website=zeetv.zee5.com|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-07}}</ref>\n* [[Shalini Pandey]] as Neelam<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bhaskar.com/entertainment/bollywood/news/bamfaad-movie-trailer-release-arjun-reddy-actress-shalini-pandeys-romantic-chemistry-with-paresh-rawals-son-aditya-127118966.html|title=\u092c\u092e\u092b\u093e\u0921\u093c \u091f\u094d\u0930\u0947\u0932\u0930 / \u092a\u0930\u0947\u0936 \u0930\u093e\u0935\u0932 \u0915\u0947 \u092c\u0947\u091f\u0947 \u0906\u0926\u093f\u0924\u094d\u092f \u0915\u0947 \u0938\u093e\u0925 \u0926\u093f\u0916\u0940 \u0905\u0930\u094d\u091c\u0941\u0928 \u0930\u0947\u0921\u094d\u0921\u0940 \u090f\u0915\u094d\u091f\u094d\u0930\u0947\u0938 \u0936\u093e\u0932\u093f\u0928\u0940 \u092a\u093e\u0902\u0921\u0947 \u0915\u0940 \u0930\u094b\u092e\u093e\u0902\u091f\u093f\u0915 \u0915\u0947\u092e\u093f\u0938\u094d\u091f\u094d\u0930\u0940|date=6 April 2020|website=Bhaskar.com}}</ref>\n* [[Vijay Varma]] as Jigar Fareedi<ref name=\"auto\">{{Cite web|url=https://telanganatoday.com/paresh-rawals-son-aditya-to-make-acting-debut-with-bamfaad|title=Paresh Rawal\u2019s Son, Aditya, To Make Acting Debut With Bamfaad|date=7 April 2020|website=telanganatoday.com}}</ref>\n* [[Jatin Sarna]] as Zahid\n* [[Sana Amin Sheikh]] as Walia\n\n== Production ==\nDirector Ranjan has earlier made a short film titled \u2018Jaan Jigar\u2019. Ajay Rai of [[Jar Pictures]] watched the short film and told him to narrate to him whatever he writes next. Ranjan met his co-writer Hanzalah Shahid after coming back from the shoot of the film \u2018[[Mukkabaaz]]\u2019. Hanzalah gave him a script to read of a different title. Ranjan read the script and got fascinated by some characters of that world which inspired him to dwell more into that world. He took those characters and some incidents and started writing a new draft from the scratch of the script and titled it \u2018BAMFAAD\u2019<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://amp.scroll.in/reel/958368/bamfaad-trailer-inter-faith-lovers-find-the-going-tough-in-zee5-film|title=\u2018Bamfaad\u2019 trailer: Inter-faith lovers find the going tough in Zee5 film|date=6 April 2020|website=scroll.in|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200413081000/https://amp.scroll.in/reel/958368/bamfaad-trailer-inter-faith-lovers-find-the-going-tough-in-zee5-film|archive-date=6 April 2020|access-date=2020-04-07}}</ref>. Bamfaad<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.livehindustan.com/entertainment/story-paresh-rawal-son-aditya-rawal-debut-film-bamfaad-trailer-release-thrlling-love-story-3132047.html|title=\u092a\u0930\u0947\u0936 \u0930\u093e\u0935\u0932 \u0915\u0947 \u092c\u0947\u091f\u0947 \u0915\u0940 \u0921\u0947\u092c\u094d\u092f\u0942 \u092b\u093f\u0932\u094d\u092e Bamfaad \u0915\u093e \u091f\u094d\u0930\u0947\u0932\u0930 \u0930\u093f\u0932\u0940\u091c, \u0926\u092e\u0926\u093e\u0930 \u0905\u0902\u0926\u093e\u091c \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u0926\u093f\u0916\u0947 \u0906\u0926\u093f\u0924\u094d\u092f|date=6 April 2020|website=livehindustan.com|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200413074249/https://www.livehindustan.com/entertainment/story-paresh-rawal-son-aditya-rawal-debut-film-bamfaad-trailer-release-thrlling-love-story-3132047.html|archive-date=13 April 2020|access-date=2020-04-07}}</ref> is a north indian slang which portrays a certain energy and it means \u2018Explosive\u2019 or \u2018Kickass\u2019<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://m.cinemaexpress.com/stories/news/2020/apr/06/bamfaad-trailer-out-aditya-rawal-shalini-pandeys-film-is-high-on-love-and-rebellion-17898.amp|title=Bamfaad trailer out: Aditya Rawal-Shalini Pandey\u2019s film is high on love and rebellion |date=6 April 2020|website=cinemaexpress.com|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200413081843/https://m.cinemaexpress.com/stories/news/2020/apr/06/bamfaad-trailer-out-aditya-rawal-shalini-pandeys-film-is-high-on-love-and-rebellion-17898.amp|archive-date=13 April 2020|access-date=2020-04-07}}</ref>. He completed the draft of the film and narrated it to Ajay and he immediately agreed to produce it.\n\nSince this was Ranjan\u2019s debut film, the budget was quite restrained. That is why he chose his hometown Kanpur as the base for shooting. His father Manmohan Chandel has played a very important part in the shoot. There were many times when the crew didn\u2019t have permission to shoot at a location, the crew used to shoot in Ranjan father\u2019s hometown as he used to get permission for the crew easily. \n\nThe principal photography of the film began on 2nd September 2018 in Kanpur and the film was wrapped on 22nd October 2018 in Lucknow. The shooting of the film got finished in a span of 45 days.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.pinkvilla.com/entertainment/news/bamfaad-trailer-paresh-rawal-s-son-aditya-shalini-pandeys-love-story-marred-violence-drama-522226?amp|title=Bamfaad Trailer: Paresh Rawal\u2019s son Aditya & Shalini Pandey's love story is marred by violence & drama|date=7 April 2020|website=pinkvilla.com|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200413081417/https://www.pinkvilla.com/entertainment/news/bamfaad-trailer-paresh-rawal-s-son-aditya-shalini-pandeys-love-story-marred-violence-drama-522226?amp|archive-date=13 April 2020|access-date=2020-04-07}}</ref>\n\n==Soundtrack==\n{{Track listing\n| total_length   = 18:46\n| extra_column\t = Singer(s)\n| title1\t= BAMFAAD TITLE TRACK\n| lyrics1 \t= [[Raj Shekhar]]\n| extra1        = [[Vishal Mishra]]\n| length1       = 2:07\n| title2        = ISHQ KA ITAR\n| lyrics2 \t= [[Raj Shekhar]]\n| extra2        = [[Vishal Mishra]]\n| length2       = 4:49\n| title3        = MUNASIB\n| extra3        = [[Vishal Mishra]] Anandi Joshi\n| lyrics3 \t= [[Raj Shekhar]]\n| length3       = 4:00\n| title4        = YAAR MERA HO MERE RUBARU\n| extra4        = [[Sukhwinder Singh]] [[Vishal Mishra]] [[Hemant Brijwasi]] Moin Sabri\n| lyrics4 \t= [[Raj Shekhar]]\n| length4       = 7:50\n}}\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External link==\n* {{IMDb title|id=11730940}}\n* [https://www.zee5.com/movies/detai