aad-trailer-inter-faith-lovers-find-the-going-tough-in-zee5-film|title=\u2018Bamfaad\u2019 trailer: Inter-faith lovers find the going tough in Zee5 film|date=6 April 2020|website=scroll.in|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200413081000/https://amp.scroll.in/reel/958368/bamfaad-trailer-inter-faith-lovers-find-the-going-tough-in-zee5-film|archive-date=6 April 2020|access-date=2020-04-07}}</ref>. Bamfaad<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.livehindustan.com/entertainment/story-paresh-rawal-son-aditya-rawal-debut-film-bamfaad-trailer-release-thrlling-love-story-3132047.html|title=\u092a\u0930\u0947\u0936 \u0930\u093e\u0935\u0932 \u0915\u0947 \u092c\u0947\u091f\u0947 \u0915\u0940 \u0921\u0947\u092c\u094d\u092f\u0942 \u092b\u093f\u0932\u094d\u092e Bamfaad \u0915\u093e \u091f\u094d\u0930\u0947\u0932\u0930 \u0930\u093f\u0932\u0940\u091c, \u0926\u092e\u0926\u093e\u0930 \u0905\u0902\u0926\u093e\u091c \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u0926\u093f\u0916\u0947 \u0906\u0926\u093f\u0924\u094d\u092f|date=6 April 2020|website=livehindustan.com|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200413074249/https://www.livehindustan.com/entertainment/story-paresh-rawal-son-aditya-rawal-debut-film-bamfaad-trailer-release-thrlling-love-story-3132047.html|archive-date=13 April 2020|access-date=2020-04-07}}</ref> is a north indian slang which portrays a certain energy and it means \u2018Explosive\u2019 or \u2018Kickass\u2019<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://m.cinemaexpress.com/stories/news/2020/apr/06/bamfaad-trailer-out-aditya-rawal-shalini-pandeys-film-is-high-on-love-and-rebellion-17898.amp|title=Bamfaad trailer out: Aditya Rawal-Shalini Pandey\u2019s film is high on love and rebellion |date=6 April 2020|website=cinemaexpress.com|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200413081843/https://m.cinemaexpress.com/stories/news/2020/apr/06/bamfaad-trailer-out-aditya-rawal-shalini-pandeys-film-is-high-on-love-and-rebellion-17898.amp|archive-date=13 April 2020|access-date=2020-04-07}}</ref>. He completed the draft of the film and narrated it to Ajay and he immediately agreed to produce it.\n\nSince this was Ranjan\u2019s debut film, the budget was quite restrained. That is why he chose his hometown Kanpur as the base for shooting. His father Manmohan Chandel has played a very important part in the shoot. There were many times when the crew didn\u2019t have permission to shoot at a location, the crew used to shoot in Ranjan father\u2019s hometown as he used to get permission for the crew easily. \n\nThe principal photography of the film began on 2nd September 2018 in Kanpur and the film was wrapped on 22nd October 2018 in Lucknow. The shooting of the film got finished in a span of 45 days.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.pinkvilla.com/entertainment/news/bamfaad-trailer-paresh-rawal-s-son-aditya-shalini-pandeys-love-story-marred-violence-drama-522226?amp|title=Bamfaad Trailer: Paresh Rawal\u2019s son Aditya & Shalini Pandey's love story is marred by violence & drama|date=7 April 2020|website=pinkvilla.com|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200413081417/https://www.pinkvilla.com/entertainment/news/bamfaad-trailer-paresh-rawal-s-son-aditya-shalini-pandeys-love-story-marred-violence-drama-522226?amp|archive-date=13 April 2020|access-date=2020-04-07}}</ref>\n\n==Soundtrack==\n{{Track listing\n| total_length   = 18:46\n| extra_column\t = Singer(s)\n| title1\t= BAMFAAD TITLE TRACK\n| lyrics1 \t= [[Raj Shekhar]]\n| extra1        = [[Vishal Mishra]]\n| length1       = 2:07\n| title2        = ISHQ KA ITAR\n| lyrics2 \t= [[Raj Shekhar]]\n| extra2        = [[Vishal Mishra]]\n| length2       = 4:49\n| title3        = MUNASIB\n| extra3        = [[Vishal Mishra]] Anandi Joshi\n| lyrics3 \t= [[Raj Shekhar]]\n| length3       = 4:00\n| title4        = YAAR MERA HO MERE RUBARU\n| extra4        = [[Sukhwinder Singh]] [[Vishal Mishra]] [[Hemant Brijwasi]] Moin Sabri\n| lyrics4 \t= [[Raj Shekhar]]\n| length4       = 7:50\n}}\n\n==